quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,"Twaa – Haa. (Aya mavara ndemamwe ezvishamiso zveQur’aan, uye hakuna kana ani zvake anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah)"
  20,2,Hatina kuburutsa Qur’aan (iri) kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti tikupe matambudziko (tikushungurudze)
  20,3,Asi kuti seyeuchidzo kune avo vanotya (Allah)
  20,4,Iburutso kubva kune vakasika nyika nematenga kumusoro-soro
  20,5,"(Allah) vane Ngoni vakakwira pamusoro peArsh (Chigaro Choumambo chinoenderana noukuru hwavo usingaperi, uye vakakwira nenzira inoenderana neumambo wavo)"
  20,6,"Zvose zviri mumatenga nemunyika, nezviri pakati pazvo nezviri pasi pevhu ndezvavo (Allah)"
  20,7,"Uye (iwe Muhammad (SAW)) ukave unotaura zvinonzwika, zvirokwazvo, (Allah) vanoziva zvakavanda nezvakanyanya kuvanda"
  20,8,Allah! Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna umwe anofanirwa kunamatwa kunze kwavo (Allah))! Mazita ose akanaka ndeavo (Allah)
  20,9,Uye nyaya yaMusa yati yambouya here kwauri
  20,10,"Apo paakaona moto ndokuti kune mhuri yake: “Mirai! Zvirokwazvo, ndaona moto, dzimweni dzenguva ndingangokuvigirai rasha (rine moto) kubva kwauri (moto iwowo), kana kuti ndowana nhungamiririro kune moto (iwowo).”"
  20,11,"Uye paakasvika kwauri (moto uya) akave anoshevedzwa (nezita kuti): “Iwe Musa!”"
  20,12,"“Zvirokwazvo, ndini Tenzi vako (Allah)! Naizvozvo kurura shangu dzako, zvirokwazvo, uri mumupata unoyera weTuwa.”"
  20,13,“Uye ndave ndinokusarudza. Naizvozvo chinzwa zvichaburutswa (kwauri).”
  20,14,"“Zvirokwazvo, ndini Allah! Laa ilaaha illaa Ana (Hakuna mumwe mwari anofanirwa kunamatwa kunze kwangu), naizvozvo iva unondinamata, uye uve unoita Swalaah (Munamato) senzira yekundiyeuka.”"
  20,15,"“Zvirokwazvo, Nguva (Zuva rekutongwa) irikuuya, uye ndiri pedo pedo nekuiviga, nokuda kwekuti munhu wese ave anotuswa (anopuhwa mubairo wake) mune izvo zvaakashingirira kuita.”"
  20,16,"“Naizvozvo uyo asingatendi mairi (Nguva) asi achitevedzera zvido zvemoyo wake, ngaasave anokutadzisa (kutenda mairi nguva iyi) kuda ungangoparara.”"
  20,17,"“Uyezve chiicho chiri muruoko rwako rwerudyi, nhai Musa?”"
  20,18,"(Musa) akati: “Iyi itsvimbo yangu, ndinoizendamira, uye ndinoikoshomoresa mashizha anozodyiwa nehwai dzangu, uye ndinowanawo zvimwe zvishando mairi.”"
  20,19,"(Allah) ndokuti: “Naizvozvo ikande pasi, iwe Musa!”"
  20,20,"Naizvozvo akaikanda pasi, chiriporipotyo yakanga yava nyoka, yaizvonyongoka nekukurumidza"
  20,21,"(Allah) ndokuti: “Itore hako uyezve usatye, tichave tinoidzosera kuchimiro chayo chokutanga.”"
  20,22,"“Uyezve dzvanyidzira ruoko rwako (rworudyi) murutivi rwako (rweruboshwe), rwuchabuda rwuchipenya rwusina kana chirwere sechimwe chiratidzo.”"
  20,23,“Nokuda kwekuti tikuratidze (zvimwe) zvezviratidzo zvedu zvikuru.”
  20,24,"“Chienda kuna Fir’aun (Farawo)! Zvirokwazvo, ava anozvitutumadza (anoita mabasa asakarurama).”"
  20,25,"(Musa) ndokuti: “Tenzi vangu! Ndivhurireiwo chipfuva changu (Ndipeiwo chivimbisiko – chokwadi, chekaniso nekugutsikana kuti ndichave ndinokunda).”"
  20,26,“Uyezve ivai munondirerutsira chisungo changu (basa rangu).”
  20,27,“Uyezve sunungurai chifundo kubva parurimi rwangu (bvisai kutadza nekukanganisa kwangu mukutaura).” (Izvi zvokutadza kutaura zvakanaka – kukama kwaMusa kwakauya nokuda kwerasha raiva nemoto raakaisa mukanwa achiri mwana mudiki)
  20,28,“Kuti vanzwisise mashoko angu.”
  20,29,“Uyezve muve munondisarudzirawo mubatsiri wangu kubva mumhuri yangu.”
  20,30,"“Haaroon (Aroni), mukoma wangu.”"
  20,31,“Ivai munowedzera simba rangu kuburikidza naye.”
  20,32,“Uyezve mubatanidzei neni pamushando wangu (wekusvitsa mashoko aAllah uye neuporofita).”
  20,33,“Kuti tive tinokurumbidzai kazhinji.”
  20,34,“Uye kuti tive tinokurangarirai kazhinji.”
  20,35,"“Zvirokwazvo, imi ndimi munenge makangotirinda.”"
  20,36,"(Allah) vakati: “Wave unopihwa zvawakumbira, iwe Musa!”"
  20,37,“Uye zvirokwazvo tave tinoita mutsa kwauri zvekare.”
  20,38,“Apo patakaburutsa kuna amai vako izvo zvatakaburutsa.”
  20,39,"“(Patakati): ‘Mugadzikei (mwana wenyu) muTaboot (Bhokisi kana kuti Mukwembe kana kuti Chityu), uye mogadzika (bhokisi racho) murwizi (rweNile), pedzezvo rwizi rwuchakanda (bhokisi iroro) kumahombekombe (kwerwizi). Muvengi wangu nemuvengi wake (Farawo) achave anomutora (kubvapo). Uyezve ndakave ndinogadzika (kanda) rudo rwangu (ini Allah) pauri, kuti ukure uri pasi peziso rangu (ndichikuchengeta).’”"
  20,40,"“Apo hanzvadzi yako payaifamba ndokubva yati: ‘Ndingakutungamirirei here kune anokwanisa kumuriritira?’ Naizvozvo takakudzosera kuna amai vako, kuti maziso avo ave anotonhorerwa uye kuti (amai vako) vasashushikane. Uyezve wakauraya munhu, asi takakubatsira kubva mumatambudziko, uye zvekare tikave tinokuedza (ne)miedzo (mikuru). Naizvozvo, wakave unogara kwemakore akati kuti nevagari vekuMadyan (Midian). Pedzezvo wauya kuno nenguva yandakakutarira, iwe Musa!”"
  20,41,“Zvekare ndave ndinozvisarudzira iwe kuti uve wangu.”
  20,42,"“Chienda iwewe nemukoma wako nezviratidzo zvedu, zvekare musave munotemberenuka mukundirangarira.”"
  20,43,"“Chiendai (muri vaviri) kuna Farawo, zvirokwazvo, (Farawo) ave anopfurikidza mwero.”"
  20,44,"“Uye motaura naye zvinyoro-nyoro, dzimweni dzenguva achatambira yeuchidzo kana kuti achatya.”"
  20,45,"Vakataura (Musa naHaaroon (Aroni)) vakati: “Tenzi vedu! Zvirokwazvo, tinotya kuti (Farawo) anganokurumidza kuti ranga kana kuti angangoita zvisakarurama kwatiri.”"
  20,46,"(Allah) vakabva vati: “Musave munotya. Zvirokwazvo, ndinenge ndinemi (muruzivo rwangu) ndichinzwa nekuona (zvese).”"
  20,47,"“Saka chiendai kwaari muri vaviri mobva mati: ‘Zvirokwazvo, tiri vatumwa vaTenzi vako (iwewe Farawo). Saka titume (tiende) nevana veIzirairi uyezve usave unovaranga. Zvirokwazvo, tauya nehumboo kubva kuna Tenzi vako (Allah). Uye runyararo ruchave pane uyo achatevedzera gwara rakaswatuka (kutenda muna Allah)!’”"
  20,48,"“Zvirokwazvo zvave zvinoburutswa kwatiri kuti chokwadi mutongo uchave pane uyo acharamba (kutenda muhumwechete hwaAllah nemuvatumwa vake), uye (uchave uri pane uyo) achashozhonoka (achafutarita chokwadi).”"
  20,49,"(Farawo) ndokuti: “Saka ndianiko Tenzi venyu muri vaviri, nhai iwe Musa?”"
  20,50,"(Musa akapindura) akati: “Tenzi vedu ndeavo vakapa chinhu chose chimiro chachona, pedzezvo ndokuchitungamira.”"
  20,51,"(Farawo) ndokuti: “Naizvozvo munotiiko nezvezvizvarwa zvokutanga (zvakare)?”"
  20,52,"(Musa) ndokupindura achiti: “Ruzivo (irworwo) pamusoro pavo rwuna Tenzi vangu mubhuku. Tenzi vangu havakanganise kana kukanganwa.”"
  20,53,"(Tenzi vangu) ndeavo vakaita kuti nyika kwamuri ive semubhedha (wakangowaridzwa), zvekare (ndiTenzi vangu) vakakuvhurirai nzira mairi, uye vakaburutsa mvura kubva kumatenga. Uye (isu Allah) takaburitsa mhando dzakasiyana siyana (ndudzi) dzezvirimwa kuburikidza nayo (mvura)"
  20,54,"Idyai uye muve munofudza zvipfuyo zvenyu! Zvirokwazvo, imomo mune maAayaat (zviratidzo) kune vanhu vanonzwisisa"